diewald_shapeFile.files.dbf
Class DBF_File

java.lang.Object
  diewald_shapeFile.files.ShapeFileReader
      diewald_shapeFile.files.dbf.DBF_File

public class DBF_File
extends ShapeFileReader

dBase File Reader (*.dbf).

extracts HEADER, FIELDS and RECORDS from a given ByteBuffer.

RECORDS: 2D-String Table:
String[row][col]... String[number of records][number of fields].

FIELDS: information about type, length, name (can be useful for converting the values).

Author:
thomas diewald (2012)
